(56120, '830974C9-88F7-4A78-BEF9-4968FACC8D83', 'We figured it out. Orli woke me at 4….talia put her to sleep in her room and she wanted to move. I re-read/listened to some of the Richard Schwartz book early this morning. The exercises help me get settled and regulated… I also helped lead one of the processes last night at mkp….which helped me get out of my head/body and being of service. I do have some reflections to share. I look forward to  peaceful and loving Shabbat with you. I love you … all of you. I understand that some of the harsh and critical words I said in the past about that part of you being a “bottomless pit” of needs…has been damaging and has made her  feel defensive and distrustful. I hope I can rebuild that trust. I’m sorry for shaming you that way.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-16T09:11:03.336356'),
(56121, '9C4B2491-342A-41B2-84E9-0E00EFBBBF20', 'Thanks love for this. I️t’s helpful to know I️’m coming home to someone loving and peaceful. I️ was listening to some of the book this morning too. The exercise is really hard for me to do solo though.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-16T10:03:06.102863'),
