(56132, '8AD81518-3FC5-4590-A9F1-EFC8A1C0B44D', 'The exercises and Parts work in general…really requires someone to facilitate. It’s really hard to get rolling without someone coaching….Would be curious to know whether your therapist does this sort of work. I can also give you a taste, if you wish, with an MKP process…I led one last night called Bucketing…which helps people resolve an issue that repeatedly comes up. .', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-16T11:12:24.903000'),
(56133, 'A4CECD31-4135-483A-83B7-56A680167705', 'I️’m open to it ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-16T11:20:36.507375'),
(56134, '34266B1E-9825-4C67-A5BE-0665C8034779', 'But I️ think it might be helpful if we get some distance from these issues for a bit a find other ways to connect. Just for a bit. Everything is so raw and you are right, we don’t have a lot of trust.  I feel like when i try to go deeper with you on these set of issues, we are in a dynamic where you are trying to persuade me to be different. And then i immediately struggle. We may just need some new fodder and life experiences to carry us for a little while and then we can come back to some of this. Just some ideas that I️’d love to consider with you. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-16T11:26:09.049636'),
(56136, 'A8807214-DE02-4022-8D5B-28DD3EAD3731', 'I can’t persuade you to be different. I am pointing out what I see, how I understand what’s going on and the impact it has on me and others.  I do wish for you to be free of issues that you find torturous and yes, I don’t want you to engage in behaviors that are hurtful. To be clear on the issue of non-monogamy. I’m no longer okay with our non-monogamy agreements to have romantic relationships with other people unless there is consent from all parties and unless it is free of conflicts of interests at work. I can’t control what you do, but I can’t support these behaviors because they are unethical. I don’t know what this means in practice, honestly, and I understand and have empathy for the fact that you have longstanding relationships here that mean a lot to you. I want to find common ground and I do not want to end our marriage…there is too much love and goodness….and I want to continue to build a life together with you. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-16T12:03:50.861000'),
(56137, '879C498C-C4D5-4F11-9F1C-2588E3916D11', 'Thanks love. I️ know all these things. And I appreciate that you understand that the people who I️ have long histories with and deep and meaningful connections to are not things I’m willing to let go of. So it would be great to figure out what common ground looks like. I️ thought that was what you were saying to me a few Thursday nights ago. And I️ would love to have that conversation.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-16T12:10:47.620464'),
