(56233, '97FA707A-C669-4584-88DB-4F8CE37EC4FD', 'Hey love, I’m good with this. I’d like to talk with you about going to the concert after dinner. Given that we are starting at 5:30, I think it should be possible to both share the day and early evening with family and friends and then have me peel off to make most of the show….which is important to me. I understand that this is uncomfortable for you and that this isn’t the best timing. I value creating these family traditions with you as well…especially around meals, as you know.  Realize this might also be a different in our upbringing…for me, RH is one day/night and it is over…while for you, this feels like I’m going out in the middle.  We can discuss later….I still have the tickets up for sale, but haven’t gotten any offers.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-19T09:56:14.186757'),
