(56260, '784A7DB4-BFEF-4A3E-9EA2-FB33E3C2B087', 'Hi love. Headed into my retreat in a short bit. Just wanted to say that I️ appreciate the ability to shift into just kinda being us this past weekend and letting some of the conflict and intensity lay low for a bit. I️ never want to sweep things under the rug, but I️’m eager to find some connection and closeness outside of non monogamy stuff. So thanks for shifting and for doing that regulation work on Thursday night so that we could be together in a loving way this weekend. I️ know what we are going through is super hard. I️ don’t take for granted that you have stretched in many ways to make it work on my behalf. It was fun to dance with you last night. And then make love while you nibbled on my neck. And it was great to declutter our house. Thank you for giving me the space to lead this retreat this week and for stepping into caretaking fully. I️ don’t take you for granted in any way. Love all of you. All of you.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-19T12:49:00.396783'),
(56273, '5B9D3095-B27A-48F3-8A2A-6E35FD20D047', 'Was wondering if you enjoyed the nibbling! Couldn’t tell for sure.  I love all of you too. And will continue to practice and learn better ways to engage while keeping grounded.  This is pretty difficult, but I know we will work through it. ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-19T15:35:46.358941');
